name: chapter IV : 𝖙𝖍𝖊 𝖕𝖆𝖈𝖙
description:
suffer again? in exchange for? 
come back or stay, can only be negotiated?
what is the price of all this? 
the eternal wait, for the choice of a path, of a backpack, Sisyphus,
What will they decide? What will I decide?
Will everything be the same again?
forgetting everything will be worth it?
This is my 45th day in here, I don't know what will happen for the forty-ninth day, will I reincarnate or will I stay?
